These two weeks will be both interminably long, and over instantly. Thereâ€™s just so much to do before you come home with us, and I canâ€™t wait until youâ€™re there. Youâ€™ll be welcomed immediately by your sister, <a href="http://www.sowrey.org/tag/DearMonkey">The Monkey</a>, by Asia the cat, and your Grandpa, whoâ€™s eagerly awaiting his next grandchild. Your second cousin &#8212; currently only known as â€œBaby Tâ€ &#8212; might be here by then.<br />
