<article id="post-2498" class="post-2498 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general tag-banff tag-hotels">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2010/01/new-years-tea/" rel="bookmark">New Year&#039;s Tea</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>The New Year is always a reason for change. It&#8217;s always a reason to do something differently than you&#8217;ve done before. It&#8217;s a time when people hold to ages-old traditions, and make efforts to start new ones. It&#8217;s a time to look back on the past, and look towards the future.<br />
And frankly, it&#8217;s a darn good reason to make a little trip out to Banff to see old friends.<br />
