<article id="post-2494" class="post-2494 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-general tag-health">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://geoff.wp/2009/12/my-boxing-day-special/" rel="bookmark">My Boxing Day special</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>I&#8217;ve had some interesting Boxing Days in my past, but perhaps today will rank as one of the strangest.<br />
This morning, we woke up when The Monkey &#8212; who has become very adept at waking up before Mommy and Daddy &#8212; came marching into our room somewhere around 7:00. We all lollygagged before getting up.<br />
That&#8217;s when I knew something was wrong. The room was spinning.<br />
